data.description: Enjoy City Life in this Spectacular and Spacious 2-Bedroom, 2-Bath SmartHome Condo! Historical Cloak Factory Building! Your Dramatic New City Address awaits Downtown and close to SO Much! Spectacular Hi-Ceilings! Gorgeous Solid Oak Hardwood flooring! You'll love the Unique Architectural Details as well as the Contemporary Touches, like the newer High-End lighting fixtures. Open and inviting layout is perfect for entertaining or just kicking back and relaxing. The kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, granite countertops and lots of counter-top and cabinet space. Spacious master bedroom features an En-Suite master bath with granite countertops. Utility room with full-sized washer and dryer that stay. Included is one assigned parking space within a secured, attached parking garage. The amenities include a state of the art fitness center, sauna and beautifully appointed roof-top deck with an outdoor kitchen. Pets allowed! Leasing allowed! Gorgeous Lake View from this massive patio located right across the hall while overlooking the exciting East Bank of the Flats, First Energy Stadium, restaurants & entertainment galore. Take advantage of this Incredible Opportunity! You'll LOVE this place! NOTE:List Agent related to Seller. SO EZ2C! Call a Realtor today.
